title: Aligarh
subTitle: Ramchandra Siras, a professor on whom a sting operation is carried out to determine his sexual orientation, forms a special bond with the journalist who covers his story.

title: Sherdil: The Pilibhit Saga
subTitle: A sacrificed village leader, Gangaram, embarks on a journey in search of a dangerous tiger that threatens people.

title: Qarib Qarib Singlle
subTitle: Jaya and Yogi, two contrasting personalities, set out to retrace past relationships, sparking the most eventful trip of their lives.

title: CityLights
subTitle: Deepak Singh, an ex-army person from Rajasthan, moves to Mumbai with his family hoping for a better lifestyle. However, upon arrival, he realises that everything is not as easy as it seems.

title: Sonchiriya
subTitle: After their leader's death, a group of dacoits splits up and runs away. On the way, they meet two women and help them escape their family and reach the hospital.

title: Udta Punjab
subTitle: A rock star, a migrant labourer, a doctor and a policeman find themselves struggling to cope with the ensuing chaos surrounding a drug crisis in Punjab, India.

title: Veere Di Wedding
subTitle: Four young women navigate love, family, and careers while supporting one another. The childhood friends are brought together for Kalindi's wedding and are forced to untangle their lives.

title: Bareilly Ki Barfi
subTitle: In the small-town of Bareilly, a free-spirited Bitti hates that she is being pressured into getting married. But when she reads a book that reflects her life, she sets out to find its author.

title: Naam Shabana
subTitle: Shabhana, desperate for justice, agrees to join a secret intelligence agency in exchange for their help in unmasking her friend's murderer.

title: Jawaani Jaaneman
subTitle: Jazz, a 40-year-old man, leads a frivolous casanova lifestyle in London. However, when Tia, a young woman claiming to be his daughter, enters his life, he decides to mend his ways.

title: Ghoomer
subTitle: A batting prodigy believes her cricketing career is over after she loses her right hand in an accident. However, a failed cricketer takes a chance on her and trains her to be a bowler instead.

title: The Accidental Prime Minister
subTitle: Amidst the political upheaval, Dr Manmohan Singh, an Indian economist, faces several challenges during his tenure as the Prime Minister of India.

title: Dhaakad
subTitle: Despite her reservations, Agent Agni takes up the mission to track and capture Rudraveer, a trafficker in India. However, the assignment soon takes her down unnavigated routes.

title: Sniff
subTitle: Sunny, who lacks the sense of smell, finds his olfactory abilities enhanced after becoming a victim of a laboratory accident, which turns him into a superhero.

title: Saheb, Biwi Aur Gangster 3
subTitle: Madhvi Devi relishes her political power but worries about losing it upon her husband Aditya's release from prison. To prevent this, she recruits Uday, a gangster, to assassinate him.

title: Akaash Vani
subTitle: During their time in college, Akaash and Vani fall for each other. But when Akaash moves to the UK for further studies, unforseen circumstances force Vani to marry Ravi, an abusive man.

title: Phobia
subTitle: A woman becomes agoraphobic after being assaulted by a taxi driver. She becomes convinced that a malevolent force has taken over the very home in which she is trapped.

title: Dil Juunglee
subTitle: Love blossoms between Koroli and Sumit, two people with contrasting personalities, when the latter joins her English class.

title: Salaam Venky
subTitle: Sujata, an ideal mother, faces the biggest challenge of her life when her son is diagnosed with muscular dystrophy. Despite this, she is determined to help her child live life to the fullest.

title: Gaami
subTitle: Shankar, a reclusive man, embarks on an adventure to the Himalayas to find a cure for a rare human condition. However, things get complicated when his past unfolds.

title: Middle Class Love
subTitle: A young college boy who is disappointed with his family's middle-class lifestyle decides to escape it by joining a popular college and having a wealthy girlfriend.

title: Rashtra Kavach Om
subTitle: A classified mission leaves a para commando with amnesia, unanswered questions and the duty of protecting his nation from terrorists. Along the way, he must find his father and prove his innocence.

title: Happy Bhag Jayegi
subTitle: Happy, a vibrant Indian girl, elopes on the day of her wedding so that she can marry Guddu, the man she loves. However, she mistakenly arrives at the home of a Pakistani politician where chaos ensues.
